object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT  
		metal_aae.source_name, 
		metal_aae.load_type, 
		metal_aae.agency_nup, 
		metal_aae.create_date, 
		metal_aae.email_address, 
		metal_aae.email_type, 
		metal_aae.group_nup, 
		metal_aae.id, 
		metal_aae.modified_date,
		current_batch.batch_id
FROM $$raw_schema.adm_agency_email metal_aae
CROSS JOIN current_batch
ORDER BY 
    metal_aae.id,
    metal_aae.create_date,
    metal_aae.modified_date;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: o_src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5('source_name' || source_name || 
	'load_type' || load_type || 
	'o_agency_email_datetime_created' || to_char(o_agency_email_datetime_created) || 
	'o_agency_email_datetime_modified' || to_char(o_agency_email_datetime_modified) || 
	'o_agency_id' || to_char(o_agency_id) ||
	'email_address' || email_address || 
	'email_type' || email_type ||
	'o_group_id' || to_char(o_group_id) || 
	'o_agency_email_id' || to_char(o_agency_email_id))

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
        adm_agency_email_row_id, 
        adm_agency_email_row_md5checksum, 
        email_address,  
        modified_date,
        id,
        adm_agency_email_row_effective_end_datetime	
    FROM $$staging_schema.adm_agency_email
    where adm_agency_email_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
